    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically just the buildup of those ions causing the pain? is there any way to stop it from happening or is it just a part of training? also how long does it usually take for the body to clear it all out once the workout is done?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
